{"tid":1262624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"現時焦點太多，繼續出割蓆分化post實屬不智","createTime":"2019-06-27T18:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T19:02:16.000Z","uid":119458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d68834de9d97601badaf9b73c799a2872b56cd8f","tid":1262624,"uid":119458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:42:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">謹記</span><br />\n我地唔係唔清算，而係留返事後再慢慢清算</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【兄弟爬山各自努力，隨時為兄弟提供清晰目標】<br />\n</strong><br />\n好多手足做決定前都會上連登望下，但連登呢幾日有大量三毛五毛湧入黎有風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />假如巴絲打們仲要繼續討論割蓆分化，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">真正<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重要而緊急</span>嘅post只會沉晒底</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【文宣組已經好多野要搞，有啲小事就<strong><ins>暫時</ins></strong>唔好麻煩佢地】</strong><br />\n<br />\n由懶人包到meme圖，再到登記選民同醫警新聞，文宣每樣都要同對家鬥快鬥多。但部分人有咩風吹草動就召喚文宣，甚至有人連fact check都交埋比文宣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重要關頭，你<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不吐不快就留返係自己IG講，仲可以順道逼啲日撚日話自己政治冷感嘅on9睇多啲新聞</span></span>，一齊關注呢幾日香港發生嘅大事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb00e82190725075f39e3792eac5443c1519365c","tid":1262624,"uid":52282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:42:55.000Z","msg":"【整合】（不斷更新）由G20到7.1嘅活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262544</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"033c29056974d931808c65784bc846d027791e51","tid":1262624,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:44:26.000Z","msg":"當香港送中條例、警察犯法嘅問題處理好時，係咪應該食住個勢對抗中共？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih